### Translate a variant for "ramme" from Danish to Russian

POST {{HostAddress}}/api/v2/Translation/LookUpWord?code={{code}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "Text": "https://ordnet.dk/ddo/ordbog?select=ramme,3&query=rammer",
